49rtc::scoped_refptr<webrtc::VideoFrameBuffer> pixelBufferToFrame(CVPixelBufferRef pixelBuffer)
50{
51 RTCCVPixelBuffer *frameBuffer = [[RTCCVPixelBuffer alloc] initWithPixelBuffer:pixelBuffer];
52 return new rtc::RefCountedObject<ObjCFrameBuffer>(frameBuffer);
53}
54
55static bool CopyVideoFrameToPixelBuffer(const webrtc::I420BufferInterface* frame, CVPixelBufferRef pixel_buffer) {
56 RTC_DCHECK(pixel_buffer);
57 RTC_DCHECK(CVPixelBufferGetPixelFormatType(pixel_buffer) == kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr8BiPlanarFullRange || CVPixelBufferGetPixelFormatType(pixel_buffer) == kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr8BiPlanarVideoRange);
58 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0), static_cast<size_t>(frame->height()));
59 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0), static_cast<size_t>(frame->width()));
60
61 if (CVPixelBufferLockBaseAddress(pixel_buffer, 0) != kCVReturnSuccess)
62 return false;
63
64 auto src_width_y = frame->width();
65 auto src_height_y = frame->height();
66 auto src_width_uv = frame->ChromaWidth();
67 auto src_height_uv = frame->ChromaHeight();
68
69 uint8_t* dst_y = reinterpret_cast<uint8_t*>(CVPixelBufferGetBaseAddressOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0));
70 int dst_stride_y = CVPixelBufferGetBytesPerRowOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0);
71 auto dst_width_y = CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0);
72 auto dst_height_y = CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0);
73
74 uint8_t* dst_uv = reinterpret_cast<uint8_t*>(CVPixelBufferGetBaseAddressOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1));
75 int dst_stride_uv = CVPixelBufferGetBytesPerRowOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1);
76 auto dst_width_uv = CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1);
77 auto dst_height_uv = CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1);
78
79 if (src_width_y != dst_width_y
80 || src_height_y != dst_height_y
81 || src_width_uv != dst_width_uv
82 || src_height_uv != dst_height_uv)
83 return false;
84
85 int result = libyuv::I420ToNV12(
86 frame->DataY(), frame->StrideY(),
87 frame->DataU(), frame->StrideU(),
88 frame->DataV(), frame->StrideV(),
89 dst_y, dst_stride_y, dst_uv, dst_stride_uv,
90 frame->width(), frame->height());
91
92 CVPixelBufferUnlockBaseAddress(pixel_buffer, 0);
93
94 if (result)
95 return false;
96
97 return true;
98}
99
100static bool CopyVideoFrameToPixelBuffer(const webrtc::I010BufferInterface* frame, CVPixelBufferRef pixel_buffer)
101{
102 RTC_DCHECK(pixel_buffer);
103 RTC_DCHECK(CVPixelBufferGetPixelFormatType(pixel_buffer) == kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr10BiPlanarVideoRange || CVPixelBufferGetPixelFormatType(pixel_buffer) == kCVPixelFormatType_420YpCbCr10BiPlanarFullRange);
104 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0), static_cast<size_t>(frame->height()));
105 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0), static_cast<size_t>(frame->width()));
106
107 if (CVPixelBufferLockBaseAddress(pixel_buffer, 0) != kCVReturnSuccess)
108 return false;
109
110 auto src_y = const_cast<uint16_t*>(frame->DataY());
111 auto src_u = const_cast<uint16_t*>(frame->DataU());
112 auto src_v = const_cast<uint16_t*>(frame->DataV());
113 auto src_width_y = frame->width();
114 auto src_height_y = frame->height();
115 auto src_stride_y = frame->StrideY();
116 auto src_width_uv = frame->ChromaWidth();
117 auto src_height_uv = frame->ChromaHeight();
118 auto src_stride_u = frame->StrideU();
119 auto src_stride_v = frame->StrideV();
120
121 auto* dst_y = reinterpret_cast<uint16_t*>(CVPixelBufferGetBaseAddressOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0));
122 auto dst_stride_y = CVPixelBufferGetBytesPerRowOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0) / 2;
123 auto dst_width_y = CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0);
124 auto dst_height_y = CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 0);
125
126 auto* dst_uv = reinterpret_cast<uint16_t*>(CVPixelBufferGetBaseAddressOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1));
127 auto dst_stride_uv = CVPixelBufferGetBytesPerRowOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1) / 2;
128 auto dst_width_uv = CVPixelBufferGetWidthOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1);
129 auto dst_height_uv = CVPixelBufferGetHeightOfPlane(pixel_buffer, 1);
130
131 if (src_width_y != dst_width_y
132 || src_height_y != dst_height_y
133 || src_width_uv != dst_width_uv
134 || src_height_uv != dst_height_uv)
135 return false;
136
137 libyuv::I010ToP010(src_y, src_stride_y,
138 src_u, src_stride_u,
139 src_v, src_stride_v,
140 dst_y, dst_stride_y, dst_uv, dst_stride_uv,
141 src_width_y, src_height_y);
142
143 CVPixelBufferUnlockBaseAddress(pixel_buffer, 0);
144 return true;
145}
146
147CVPixelBufferRef pixelBufferFromFrame(const VideoFrame& frame, const std::function<CVPixelBufferRef(size_t, size_t, BufferType)>& makePixelBuffer)
148{
149 auto buffer = frame.video_frame_buffer();
150 if (buffer->type() != VideoFrameBuffer::Type::kNative) {
151 auto type = buffer->type();
152 if (type != VideoFrameBuffer::Type::kI420 && type != VideoFrameBuffer::Type::kI010) {
153 RTC_LOG(WARNING) << "Video frame buffer type is not expected.";
154 return nullptr;
155 }
156
157 auto pixelBuffer = makePixelBuffer(buffer->width(), buffer->height(), type == VideoFrameBuffer::Type::kI420 ? BufferType::I420 : BufferType::I010);
158 if (!pixelBuffer) {
159 RTC_LOG(WARNING) << "Pixel buffer creation failed.";
160 return nullptr;
161 }
162
163 if (type == VideoFrameBuffer::Type::kI420)
164 CopyVideoFrameToPixelBuffer(buffer->GetI420(), pixelBuffer);
165 else
166 CopyVideoFrameToPixelBuffer(buffer->GetI010(), pixelBuffer);
167 return pixelBuffer;
168 }
169
170 auto *frameBuffer = static_cast<ObjCFrameBuffer*>(buffer.get())->wrapped_frame_buffer();
171 if (![frameBuffer isKindOfClass:[RTCCVPixelBuffer class]])
172 return nullptr;
173
174 auto *rtcPixelBuffer = (RTCCVPixelBuffer *)frameBuffer;
175 return rtcPixelBuffer.pixelBuffer;
176}
